## Holy Help Tab
If you wanna figure out how to do more things, check out the Markdown Quick Reference.

There's also a Keyboard Shortcuts Reference in there.

For more YAML customizations see this [link](https://bookdown.org/yihui/rmarkdown/html-document.html).

## Wanna write some equations?

$$
Y{ij} = \beta_0 + \beta_1 + \epsilon_i
$$

If you'd like to make it inline, use one '\$' instead of two: $\hat{\beta}_0$.

Btw, see 'bookdown' package for advanced HTML options.

